  <brief_title>Study of 0444 Gel in the Treatment of Inflammatory Lesions of Rosacea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Vehicle-Controlled, Parallel Group Study of 0444 Gel</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Fougera Pharmaceuticals Inc.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Fougera Pharmaceuticals Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this trial is to assess the efficacy of Metronidazole Topical Gel 1% in the
      Treatment of Inflammatory Lesions of Rosacea.

      Treatment medication will be administered as follows: A thin film of gel will be applied and
      rubbed into the entire face once daily for a period of 70 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
