  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of rosacea

          -  Good health with the exception of rosacea

          -  Papsules and pustules minimum and maximum requirements

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are pregnant, nursing, or planning a pregnancy within the study
             participation period.

          -  Subjects who have any systemic or dermatological disorders with the exception of
             rosacea
